      <akn:section eId="sec_28_3906">
        <akn:num>28-3906</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Consumer education and information.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_28-3906_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Office of Consumer Protection is established within the Department. The Office of Consumer Protection shall:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_28-3906_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The Chief of the Office of Consumer Protection shall be appointed by the Director.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_28-3906_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>In fiscal year 2006, the Office of Consumer Protection shall focus on investigation and mediation in the areas of auto repair and home improvement.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
